---
title: Brown Sugar-Glazed Double Salmon with Garlic Rice and Sugar Snap Peas
description: The combo of roasted salmon and fluffy rice is always a hit, and we know your family will really love the sweet and savoury flavours in this dish. Dinner tonight features salmon glazed in sauce made from brown sugar, soy sauce and hoisin sauce, and the rice is boosted with garlic.
